name: fossasia
tagline: A program made using lighttable IDE for FOSSASIA
body:
This site is dedicated to my lighttable program which is just a simple Alarm clock. This is just a simple page I created for FOSSASIA's another task which is "Learn Git". I loved the modules but I wished the course had been a little shorter. But anyways the tutorial was well explaining. I hope this task is complete with this page as well as it was a bit long task to see all those modules.

Bye
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
